Proposal Factory is suggesting that they will add value to the Cardano Ecosystem by improving access to Catalyst in the form of intentional workshops in the lead up to Catalyst Funding rounds and provide faster feedback and support to new proposers. 

The proposal is not specifically addressing funding mechanisms outside of Catalyst, rather how to demystify Catalyst for new proposers. For this reason it might not be in the right category.; 

The impact is global in the sense that it is delivered online, however it is not directly addressing global in terms of cultural diversity and need requirements in terms of language and addressing barriers such as that in the onboarding process.
